I have definitely experienced better. The service is VERY slow. After realizing the inside dining room was small and stuffy, I asked to sit outside. Despite the server only having 1 table with 2 people, it took 10 minutes for someone to locate me outside, and prior to that they didn't even offer us drinks. The dining experience outside was nice, however the service continued to be very slow.  Once we received the food (which we ordered medium hot), it was too spicy to eat. Instead of sending the food back, we got it in a to go box.  Only go here if you're willing to take 2 hours for a meal.

